Text.SourceString: Are you reeeeeally the new person?//Dad said you were a farmer. Is that right? What kinda farming tools do you have?//<portrait=normal>Okay, I believe you. Why don’t you look like a farmer, though?
My Uncle <NPCName>Surya</> is new too.//<portrait=happy>Just like you!
My mom makes the best fish tacos! That’s my favorite kind of taco.
Can you do stuff like that?
<NPCName>Macy</> lives at the inn, and she has a pet lobster. I’ve seen it lots of times and…uh…<NPCName>Stephen</>, I think.//Yeah, his name is <NPCName>Stephen</>.
This one time, she let me pet it!
I like playing in the forest. It’s close to my house, and it doesn’t get too hot. But I’m not allowed to go there by myself. So I have to wait for dad to get out of work.
Mom said I’ll be a great vet when I grow up because I love animals.
Umm… No, thanks. I don’t want to be a farmer…//I don’t like gardening that much.
I want to grow up really fast. I want to be as big as my dad… Or Uncle <NPCName>Surya</>.//So I can reach things.
I still have to use a ladder to reach stuff…
What are you going to do today? I have school today and tomorrow, so…
I have to wake up at 7 in the morning… Every day… Ugh. That way, I’m not late for school.
Err…yeah?
I think I’ll go and play with <NPCName>Surya</> tomorrow at the Vineyard.
Or maybe just on Sunday… I’m not sure. I’m gonna see if my friends want to fly kites tomorrow.
I like playing in the forest. It’s close to my house, and it doesn’t get too hot.//But I’m not allowed to go there by myself. So I have to wait for dad to get out of work.
I think I’ll go and play with <NPCName>Taco</> tomorrow at the Vineyard.
<NPCName>Taco</> comes from the forest. I wonder what other kinds of animals live there? Oh, no… Not the part where <NPCName>Ben</> parks, but the forest-forest…
Do you think there are big bears or…long snakes?!
<NPCName>Macy</> lives at the inn, and she has a pet lobster. I’ve seen it lots of times and…uh…<NPCName>Stephen</>, I think. Yeah, his name is <NPCName>Stephen</>.
<NPCName>Macy</> said <NPCName>Stephen</> is sick, though, so… Hope he gets better soon.
Sometimes <NPCName>Oliver</> lends me his detective comic books.//He’s so nice!
I wonder if I can be a kid detective too… I could, but I don’t wanna.
Art is so much fun. One time, we made lots of useful things from water bottles we found around the island.
I collect trash I see in the forest, but there isn’t much there.
One day, I wanna cure all diseases so no animals can get sick, ever!
I told Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</> I want to be a vet when I grow up and learn more about all sorts of animals.
He said that Coral Island can use a vet, and as long as I still love animals and keep reading, I’ll be a great vet someday.
Mom packs me lunch every day. She usually makes a lot of food in one go… And then she gives me the same thing for three days.
It gets boring… But I don’t mind. It’s always yummy.
I can’t play with my friends after school today because I wanna hunt mushrooms with Dad in the forest!
Umm… No, I don’t have a favorite mushroom, because they’re gross!//It’s only fun looking for them.
I can’t play with my friends after school today because I wanna hunt mushrooms with Dad in the forest!
It’s gonna be so much fun!
This one time, we caught soooo many fish, and Mom made a bunch of fish tacos for the whole class to share!
Mom likes to make bouquets with flowers that Dad and me bring home.
They’re so pretty. Mom likes pretty things.
This one time, we caught soooo many fish, and Mom made a bunch of fish tacos for the whole class to share!
…Um… Hi.
You own the farm by the forest, right?
Crickets sleep in their hideout during the day and look for food at night… I think they like peace and quiet, like my Uncle <NPCName>Surya</>.
Do you know that each cricket sings a different song? They sound the same to me, but <NPCName>Kenny</> told me our ears aren’t sensitive enough to tell them apart.
My Uncle <NPCName>Surya</> works at the lab. He’s a supersmart scientist, you know! He wrote a book and stuff.
He took me to the lab one time and let me play with his scientist stuff. It was so cool.
My favorite superhero is Zinco-man. He’s supersmart! And super-rich. Anything he wants, he can make it.
Can you make anything you want?
I like reading comic books better than watching superheroes on TV. I can take my time with books… But the library doesn’t have many comic books.
Do you know that each cricket sings a different song? They sound the same to me, but <NPCName>Kenny</> told me our ears aren’t sensitive enough to tell them apart.
Did you know that plants eat too? They need the help of the sunshine.
You have to make sure to water your crops every day because they won’t grow if you don’t.
I want a hat like Mayor <NPCName>Connor</>’s. He always has that fancy flower on it too.
I don’t get a runny nose in the Spring, but my stomach does hurt a little when I drink too much milk.
It’s sad, because it tastes good.
Oh, there must be lots of frogs on your farm, huh? Supercool!
There are lots of frogs by <NPCName>Ben</>'s caravan when it rains. Well, I don’t know for sure, because Dad doesn’t let me go there when it rains.//But we usually see more frogs after rainy days.
I have lots of treasures in my room. I found most of them in the forest.
Sometimes I get treasures from fishing too. I like getting weird-looking twigs better than getting fish.
Crickets are my favorite Summer bugs.
<NPCName>Kenny</> said we should keep our distance from them, because they can sense sound and vibration. We don’t wanna spook them.
Okay, don’t tell anyone, okay? I saw <NPCName>Taco</> playing with some bugs last weekend. But then, when I looked again, the bugs were gone.
Do you think he ate them?
Crickets sleep during the day and look for food at night… Pretty cool, huh?
Do you know that each cricket sings a different song? They sound the same to me, but <NPCName>Kenny</> told me our ears aren’t sensitive enough to tell them apart.
I have to be careful with some of the stuff I find in the forest. Because some things are dangerous to eat… Even to touch.
Do you plant cacti on your farm? The one that grows pretty flowers?
At school we learned that in winter, you can plant dragon fruit.//It’s a different kind of cactus, and it grows fruit!
I had a lot of fun carving a pumpkin with Dad… Now it’s snowball-fight time!
We aren’t allowed to bring the snow indoors at school. It’s a mess or something like that. Ugh…
Do you have any Winter wishes?
That’s not exciting… Well, I hope you get it!
Mrs. <NPCName>Bree</> is hosting a gift exchange. I hope you get it!
Mrs. <NPCName>Bree</> is hosting a gift exchange. I hope you get it!
I wish the snowmen would never melt.
I worked so hard on them… They make really cool Winter decorations.
Dragonfruit trees look like a big man with long hair that sprouts fruit. My uncle has plenty of them on his farm.//Do you have any on yours?
I wish my hair could sprout fruit!
I’m only allowed to go to the Winter fair with my parents.//They said they didn’t want me getting lost in the crowd.
I wanna go on a hot air balloon ride someday and take my whole family with me.
Not now, though. When I’m old enough!
I’m sleepyyyyyyy…
Hmmm… What? I wanna take a nap.
I hope it doesn’t storm tomorrow. I’m scared of lightning…
Oh, I have those same boots as yours. I hate them.//But sometimes Mom makes me wear them because they’re warm.
Did your mom also make you wear those boots?
I’m sleepyyyyyyy…
Hmmm… What? I wanna take a nap.
I hope it doesn’t storm tomorrow. I’m scared of lightning…
Aww… The ground is gonna be all muddy tomorrow…
I wonder if Mom will still make me wear rubber boots… I can’t walk in those.
Why are you out so late in the rain, <PlayerName>$honorifics $player</>?
Did your mom also make you wear those boots?
I’m sleepyyyyyyy… It’s storming outside. I just want to nap.
Oh, I have those same boots as yours. I hate them.//But sometimes Mom makes me wear them because they’re warm.
Did your mom also make you wear those boots?
Yay! It’s snowing!
*brrr* So cold… It makes me want to have some ice cream. Hmm…
Yay! It’s snowing! Snowball-fight time. I just gotta find somebody to play with.
Hey, you’re someone! Do you wanna have a snowball fight?
Yay! It’s snowing!
Your boots are dirty.
*humming “It’s your best birthday yet” song*
I’m gonna pack some snow and bring it home to Mom. She’s gonna be so happy!
Yay! It’s snowing! Snowball-fight time. I just gotta find somebody to play with.
Hey, you’re someone! Do you wanna have a snowball fight?
It’s snowing outside…
Snow month means birthday month!
Mom lets me watch TV after school on Fridays. On normal days, I usually go with Dad to the forest until dinnertime.
No, not the part that’s by your house. We go exploring in the other side of the forest…
What are you doing here, <PlayerName>$honorifics $player</>? Are you gonna talk about farming?
We helped Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</> decorate the classroom. We even made the decorations ourselves.
Today is supercool! I saw a couple of butterflies on my way to school. I think I’m going to draw them for my art project.
<NPCName>Kira</> told me that if you go deep enough into the forest, there are monsters that look like bouncing coconuts.
She said not to worry, because they don’t like the sunlight, so they won’t go out… They also like to live in a damp place.
Ha…ha…ha…
Did you see that, <PlayerName>$honorifics $player</>?
HA HA HA! Look! Look!
Aah… Where is my dad? We need to head to the woods before it gets too dark.
I’m so bored. I wanna go to the forest already!
I want a snack.
<NPCName>Kenny</> can talk to animals! I’ve seen him do it…
He’s so cool!
I’m learning how to fish with Dad.
Dad said if we bring home some fish, it’s great, but if we don’t, that’s okay too because we have fun.
I need to be careful walking around here. I don’t want to crush anything by accident.
My binoculars are no use around here. There isn’t anything mysterious to look at.//Everything is easy to spot.
The forest, though… Now that place has a lot of fun things to see.
<NPCName>Taco</> is a smart dog. I want a dog that’s smart like that, and we both can go on adventures in the forest!
I should’ve brought my kite!
Wanna try to fly a kite? It’s so easy here because the wind is so strong.
I only like to come here in the Summer. The wind is still too cold in the Spring…
You’re not supposed to be loud.
I go on adventures in the forest after school with Dad… But not today.//I’m gonna play here today.
We only go when it isn’t raining, though. Dad said the rain makes the ground too slippery, and it’s not safe.
I made the kites myself! Dad taught me how to make them at first, but then I had a lot of practice after that.
Don’t tell Mom, but I always give my apples to <NPCName>Taco</>.
Oh, don’t worry. I asked <NPCName>Kenny</> about it, and he said that dogs can have apples.//And Kenny is an expert in animals, you know.
I have the sniffles.
*Aachoo!*
My mom said I’ll be a great vet when I grow up because I love animals.
Umm… No, thanks. I don’t want to be a farmer… I don’t like gardening that much.
I’m only allowed to go to the Winter fair with my parents. They said they didn’t want me getting lost in the crowd.
Whoa! You found it!
So it wasn’t stolen after all?! I’ll be more careful next time. Thanks for the help, <PlayerName>$honorifics $player</>.
